org.safs.abbot

Class ATestRecordData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.TestRecordData
      • org.safs.rmi.engine.RMITestRecordData
        • org.safs.abbot.ATestRecordData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ATestRecordData
extends RMITestRecordData
implements java.io.Serializable
    Extends TestRecordData, which holds key data used by remote Abbot Agents. This is different from ATestRecordHelper used on the LocalServer side of the Engine. Must be Serializable for Abbot RMI transmission. Based on the SAFS Test Record Data doc.
    Since:
    FEB 10, 2005
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
